lead_paragraph: Hall of Famer Juli Inkster shot a 4-under 68 on Saturday for a share of the first-round lead in the Legends Tour's season-opening Walgreens Charity Classic.

headline.print_headline: Juli Inkster Tied for Lead in Legends Tour Opener
